## Development

### Prerequisites

- Rust 1.75+
- Python 3.7+
- Node.js 18+ (for examples)

### Build from Source

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/loonghao/auroraview.git
cd auroraview

# Install Rust dependencies and build
cargo build --release

# Install Python package in development mode
pip install -e .
```

### Run Tests

```bash
# Rust tests
cargo test

# Python tests
pytest tests/
```

